description: “No es esto o lo otro. Hagamos lo que hagamos somos la misma cosa. Todo pasa por el miedo; y el único miedo que conocemos es el que inventamos nosotros." Vicente Luy   //  This piece started with the creation of a virtual space which I reinterpreted with oil on canvas. The final digital image was built combining different stages of the physical painting. // First collector gets access to the physical painting (150x150 cm oil on canvas).
